Product description

INTRODUCTION:

  • Smart replacement thermostat with app control

FEATURES:

  • Remote control with the YoLink app
  • Alexa/Google Assistant and IFTTT integration
  • Unique heating/cooling schedule for each day of the week
  • Color LCD display with customizable color schemes
  • User-friendly on-screen settings menu
  • ECO Energy Conservation Operation saves you money on power bills
  • 24 VAC systems only
  • Works with most one-stage heating/cooling systems in the U.S. and Canada
  • Five wire system with C Common wire required
  • YoLink Hub required

BENEFITS:

  • Save money on your power bills by scheduling your heating/cooling temperatures to automatically adjust based on the day of the week and time of day; automatically raise the cooling set temperature to a higher setting while you are at work
  • Use the convenient YoLink app to check and change your thermostats temperature and mode, anytime from anywhere
  • Enable the ECO feature to automatically adjust set temperatures for savings on your power bill ideal for when you are away
  • Voice control with Alexa and Google Assistant integration
  • Create custom automation with IFTTT integration

SUGGESTED PRODUCTS:

  • YoLink Hub is required. Starting your first YoLink system? Consider one of our kits
  • Know the temperature and humidity levels in any room of your home with the YoLink Temperature & Humidity Sensor

REQUIREMENTS:

  • YoLink Hub with an internet connection (wired Ethernet or 2.4GHz Wi-Fi). Refer to the Hub user guide for additional information
  • Smartphone or tablet running iOS 9 or higher, Android 4.4 or higher
  • Existing wiring with at least 5 conductors, including a C Common wire
  • Tools Required, Including but Not Limited to: Drill, Phillips/cross screwdriver, small slotted screwdriver, optional mounting anchors
  • Installation Difficulty Level: Medium-to-Difficult (May require installation by an electrician or experienced installer if a C common wire is not existing)

TECHNICAL SPECS:

  • Semtech LoRa RF Module YL09 microcontroller with 32-Bit RISC processor
  • Multi-color LCD Display
  • Control Buttons (6)
  • Power: 24 VAC (From HVAC system or customer-supplied transformer)
  • Color: White
  • Dimensions (L x W x D): 5.12 x 3.58 x 0.55 inches (130 x 91 x 14 mm)
  • Scheduled Temperature Range: 32F 90F (16C 32C)
  • Detection Temperature Range: 14F 122F, 0.54F (-10C 50C, 0.3C)
  • Detection Humidity Range: 0 100%, +/- 3%
  • ECO Setting Range: 2F 9F (1C 5C)
  • Calibration Range: 0F 9F (0C 5C)
  • Environmental:
  • Operating Temperature Range: 14F 122F (-10C 50C)
  • Operating Humidity Range: 0 95% non-condensing
  • Intended for indoor use only

PACKAGE CONTENTS:

  • (1) YoLink Thermostat
  • (1) Mounting Base
  • (2) Wall Screws
  • (2) Anchors
  • (1) Quick Start Guide

    As a huge fan of the YoLink ecosystem, most of my smart devices are from this brand. So, when I noticed they offered a thermostat, I immediately swapped out my previous one. Like all YoLink products, the setup process was incredibly easy. Installation was straightforward but did require some wiring adjustments to my HVAC system (though this is typical for any thermostat installation).

    This thermostat has all the key features youd expect from a smart thermostat: the ability to adjust the temperature, control the fan, select the operating mode, and set schedulesall from the YoLink app. Ive also integrated it into Home Assistant through the YoLink integration for even more control.

    To wrap up, this is another fantastic product from YoLink. And just to clarify, Im not getting paid for this review! (Though if YoLink is listening, feel free to reach out )
